british minist criticis propos ec oil tax a british minist said that a propos european commun tax on veget oil and fat would rais the price of fish and chip and he pledg the govern would fight against it . lord belstead , a junior agricultur minist , told the hous of lord the tax would rais the price of raw materi use in mani process food by about 100 pct . he said revenu should not be rais by tax the consum and call the propos `` repugn . ''